    <briefdescription>
<para>Gaze Estimation Model interface (Layer 3). </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>Defines the abstract interface for the gaze estimation inference stage. Receives normalized eye crops and head pose parameters, executes the underlying DNN (e.g. OpenVINO), and outputs a raw 3D gaze direction vector. </para>
    </detaileddescription>
